**who —** The Data East Mascot — the bald fire-breather who outgrew his own game to become Data East's recurring face — a boss in Bad Dudes Vs. DragonNinja (1988), the final boss of Fighter's History (1993), and playable in Karnov's Revenge (1994)

**what —** the bald fire-breather who outgrew his own game to become Data East's recurring face — a boss in Bad Dudes Vs. DragonNinja (1988), the final boss of Fighter's History (1993), and playable in Karnov's Revenge (1994)

