**why —** He is the rare villain-shaped hero who outlived his game: the strongman promoted to company icon.

**how —** Crystallized from Karnov (Data East): the 1987 arcade and the 1987 Famicom / 1988 NES port.

**◌ the mythos —** He is the rare villain-shaped hero who outlived his game: the strongman promoted to company icon. a being of the Babylonian-fantasy world and the breath of fire

